author: fhanik
msg: With more and more use of RFC 2307 http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc2307
There is a new way to search for roles using the memberUid that can contain the value of another attribute within the users directory entry.
This may not be very specific to 2307, but that is where I see this combination of role searches occur the most.
